original_data.title: Tunebot
original_data.description: The dataset is a collection of 10,000 sung contributions to the Tunebot search engine. Each contribution is a recording of a contributor singing a song to Tunebot. In addition to the 10,000 contributions, there is an associated Google spreadsheet to look up the artist, album, and song for any file.
